<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.4">
<l>poruntumāmara mēḻumeytapu ṉitaṉār</l>
<l>tiruntucēvaṭi yeṉmaṉattuni ṉaitoṟum</l>
<l>karuntaṇmā kaṭalkaṅkulārk kumatuvaṉṟiyum</l>
<l>varuntavāṭai varumitaṟkiṉi yeṉceykēṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[With] every thought in my mind of the perfect rosy feet</l>
<l>Of the pure one who shot seven great adjacent trees,</l>
<l>The cold, dark, vast ocean roars at night; besides that,</l>
<l>The north wind comes up so that [I] suffer. Now what do I do for that?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
